OL,7,FThe National Education Union (NEU)
OL,8,Fhas urged its members to reject the
OL,9,FGovernment's latest pay offer for
OL,10,Fteachers in England, stoking fears
OL,11,Fthat strike action could rumble on
OL,12,Finto exam season and spell further
OL,13,Fchaos for schools.
OL,15,FThe Government has offered teachers a
OL,16,Ffresh pay package, which includes a
OL,17,Fone-off #1,000 cash payment this year
OL,18,Fand a 4.3 per cent rise for most
OL,19,Fteachers next year ` well below
OL,20,Funions' demands of an above-inflation
OL,21,Fpay offer.
